{"tid":1909915,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"外交部 : 個別媒體妄稱新冠病毒是中国病毒別有用心  中方堅決反對","createTime":"2020-03-04T09:49:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T10:56:26.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"947c55127463afa9afbf10c47b44e77e1031cdca","tid":1909915,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T09:49:50.000Z","msg":"在北京, 外交部發言人趙立堅, 批評有個別媒體稱新冠病毒是「中國病毒」, 極不負責任, 中方對此堅決反對.<br />\n<br />\n        趙立堅強調, 世界衛生組織已多次表示, 新冠病毒是全球現象, 源頭仍不確定, 此時應關注如何應對遏制病毒, 應避免地域的污名化語言. 中國權威呼吸病專家鐘南山也曾表示, 疫情首先出現在中國, 但不一定發源在中國.<br />\n<br />\n        趙立堅又說, 個別媒體在沒有任何事實依據的情況下, 妄稱新冠病毒是中國病毒, 企圖讓中國背上製造疫情災害的黑鍋, 完全是別有用心. 他說, 在疫情面前, 需要的是科學、理性、合作, 用科學戰勝愚昧, 用合作抵制偏見.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/News/live.aspx?NewsId=20200304172631\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2FNews%2Flive.aspx%3FNewsId%3D20200304172631&d=VxC68O7S0S1nNKmf4pYeId5VMZmAwfp0CD4JwUII9h4%3D&h=8798074a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/News/live.aspx?NewsId=20200304172631</a>"},{"pid":"0ad9a90b8ab429036a7aa8928760270c00b13a24","tid":1909915,"uid":3457,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T09:50:58.000Z","msg":"一世都武漢肺炎 唔洗諗喇"},{"pid":"a2e2731aa5b8baba41e9057f6e92010814307278","tid":1909915,"uid":1482,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T09:51:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ed5eT0g.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEd5eT0g.gif&h=ded528e8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"53f3632436f51f362c11eff694e1422c1c6f15c6","tid":1909915,"uid":155095,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T09:52:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">習近平肺炎</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EQJATwbUYAA4mqC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEQJATwbUYAA4mqC.jpg&h=ffba6ba1&s={S